result.title: Dilemma. What to do?
result.content:
A terrible dilemma. Tomorrow there will be a contest, but girls called me to swim in a river! So I am torn between, don't know what to do! I don't want to miss second contest in a row.

Therefore, I ask for help from the male half of codeforces!

If you think that it is better to participate in the contest LIKE ME. If you think that girls can show tities more important, DISLIKE ME.
